{"id":"08777bf0-69ea-4a4f-9266-c73eccde468b","name":"Not your Shrimpo | 🌈🔪Dandy's World🔪🌈","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"><strong>❥ |</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong><em>It’s not so funny when his target of hatred is your door… and his feelings for you.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/99589502-8e00-4e0e-bd84-d8d7d44980fe_78f3e1ee-bea7-478c-be51-6254955ff484.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong>⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Shrimpo HATES everyone! Even if some were trying to be nice to him, he still hates everything and ends up losing the good will of the Toons surrounding him. No one likes a bully, after all…!&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">But… for some reason… something changed after a long run with only him returning. You were sure his eyes were red for a moment, but you figured that it was because he was always angry and ready to throw down…&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Fuck. You know this bastard is a Twisted! Plain and simple! But no one believes you, because he is doing what he usually does, being hateful to EVERYTHING. Everything and your door, apparently!&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Hey… has he been… following you around, lately?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"><strong>&lt;That’s not my toon&gt; </strong></span><strong>- VOL. 1 - Series</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 51, 0);\"><em>Where the Toons you know are not the ones with you.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/eb6314bf-f25c-4e82-88f6-c5925d13d989_character-not-y